Description: 
        GitRemote
        
        A simple tool to add git remotes effortlessly
        
        1. pip install gitremote
        2. gitremote -i | gitremote --init
            It will create gitremote.yml
            Add remote and host
        3. gitremote -r | gitremote --reset
        
        That's it
        
